# Keys Directory

This directory stores the EC P-256 key pair used for signing JWT tokens.

## Files
- `private_key.pem` - EC P-256 private key (auto-generated on first run)
- `public_key.pem` - EC P-256 public key (auto-generated from private key)

⚠️ **Security Note**: Keys are auto-generated and stored here. In production, use proper key management solutions (HSM, KMS, etc.).
